00:59:18.918 --> 00:59:28.286
Lord, You'll help me figure it out. 'Is there something wrong with the gas?'That's what I'm talking about. Talk to Him about everything.

00:59:28.287 --> 00:59:36.404
Practice that He is standing right there with you because He dwells on the inside of you and He'll tell you and teach you about all things.

00:59:36.405 --> 00:59:40.692
Even things you don't even realize that He loves. He just wants a friend.

00:59:40.693 --> 00:59:48.971
